    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and accepted on the basis that the ASTM F1717 quasi-static protocol is the regulatory standard for this device class and that the three QoI validation metrics all pass the E/uval < 1.96 criterion with margin. The overall credibility profile supports medium assurance for a model risk level 3 COU with medium decision consequence.",
